    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "you may see as many as three flying discs from one electric",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "light bulb, which may have more or less of a ball shape. These",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "discs many times appear as inverted saucers, and if you will",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "change your position slowly you will see that they change their",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "position also. Those are best observed in the late afternoon",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "or between sun down and dusk, when it appears to you that you",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "are merely looking through the window pane at the discs sus-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "pended in the distance. As darkness comes on, the window pane",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "becomes a more perfect mirror and your discs appear as reflect-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "ions in a mirror.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "To watch the discs, through your ventilation wing, sail",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "along with you as you drive through the country, becomes very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "fascinating, especially if you use a little imagination. It",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "may absorb your thoughts completely, therefore, I would admon-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "ish automobile drivers watching the flying discs, to be cautious",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "and not run off the road or into some other car.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Some of the reports on flying saucers, heretofore not ex-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "plained in this article, such as those reported seeing bright",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "flashes in the sky, were no doubt reflected sun-light from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "planes. These light beams chanced to cross the line of vision",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "of the observer. They frequently appear very brilliant and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
